  - name: Claw.
    value: ' Melee Weapon Attack: +12 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 17 (2d10
      + 6) slashing damage. '
    category: Actions
  - name: Roar (3/Day).
    value: ' The sphinx emits a magical roar. Each time it roars before finishing
      a long rest, the roar is louder and the effect is different, as detailed below.
      Each creature within 500 feet of the sphinx and able to hear the roar must
      make a saving throw. '
    category: Actions
  - name: First Roar.
    value: ' Each creature that fails a DC 18 Wisdom saving throw is frightened for
      1 minute. A frightened creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each
      of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. '
    category: Actions
  - name: Second Roar.
    value: ' Each creature that fails a DC 18 Wisdom saving throw is deafened and
      frightened for 1 minute. A frightened creature is paralyzed and can repeat
      the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself
      on a success. '
    category: Actions
  - name: Third Roar.
    value: ' Each creature makes a DC 18 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save,
      a creature takes 44 (8d10) thunder damage and is knocked prone. On a successful
      save, the creature takes half as much damage and isn''t knocked prone.'
    category: Actions
  - name: other
    value: 'The sphinx can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below.
      Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end
      of another creature''s turn. The sphinx regains spent legendary actions at
      the start of its turn. '
    category: Legendary Actions
  - name: Claw Attack.
    value: ' The sphinx makes one claw attack. '
    category: Legendary Actions
  - name: Teleport (Costs 2 Actions).
    value: ' The sphinx magically teleports, along with any equipment it is wearing
      or carrying, up to 120 feet to an unoccupied space it can see. '
    category: Legendary Actions
  - name: Cast a Spell (Costs 3 Actions).
    value: ' The sphinx casts a spell from its list of prepared spells, using a spell
